name: Sales Force
tag_list: staffing, sales, professionals, pros, tacoma, seattle, olympia, employers, employment, agency
overview:
Sales Force provides Western Washington employers in many different industries with sales professionals of all experience levels.

Sales Force operates on a proactive approach to identifying candidates for our clients. We pre-screen and pre-qualify candidates to know what kind of positions they are looking for, where they are willing to work, and how much they expect to earn. Sales Force runs all job postings by our candidates prior to submitting their resumes. Each candidate works with a dedicated recruiter to ensure quality of service.

Sales Force builds relationships with clients in order to best fulfill their needs. We provide the top 6-8 best fit candidate resumes to employers for their job openings. Sales Force also analyzes market information in order to help make clients’ searches for sales personnel more efficient. We provide drug, background, and driving record screening upon request to round out the hiring process.

Additionally, Sales Force offers a resource page on the company website to help both candidates and employers. Sales professionals and hiring managers may find articles, sample documents, and other resources there.
